So i didn’t get to discuss how I could be involved in Max’s life this weekend. Even though I signed up for a school event that you took over, leveraging
the RO. That was a bummer that I thought we could resolve after we cleared the air yesterday. You did not.

Another week passes. Another week of complete and utter parental alienation. I understand in your mind it’s justified and even though we were all
amazing together before you started this. Somehow this transition to “no father figure” is healthy parenting.
